# Data (keep samples only, never raw datasets)
# Not root-anchored: the synthetic generator's own README has always documented running it from
# backend/ (`cd backend && make seed-synthetic ...`), which writes to backend/datasets/synthetic/
# -- a root-anchored `datasets/synthetic/` never matched that real output path.
datasets/raw/
**/datasets/synthetic/
*.parquet
*.sqlite

# ML artifacts
*.pkl
*.joblib
mlruns/
